---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Biohacking Coach Lakeway TX | EmpowerX3 Body Mind Spirit"
  description="EmpowerX3 is Lakeway's biohacking wellness center. 90-day transformation coaching, ExoPod 10-in-1 recovery therapy, and Wolfpack group hikes. Gary Brandt, biohacking & medical weight loss coach."
>

  <!-- ─── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative bg-stone-950 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] opacity-5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <!-- Subtle green glow bottom-left -->
    <div class="absolute -bottom-32 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-900/30 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <!-- Gold glow top-right -->
    <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-72 h-72 bg-gold-900/20 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-28 md:py-36">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-gold-500 font-heading font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-5">
          Lakeway, TX · Biohacking · Medical Weight Loss · Life Coaching
        </p>
        <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-tight mb-6 text-cream-100">
          A Biohacking Coach Who Lets Your Body Lead Your Healing
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-5 max-w-2xl">
          Something's off with life. You're wildly successful in one or two areas, but something isn't clicking.
          You've tried keto, bought the supplements, hired the coaches. You know what you want to change.
          And you're still stuck.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gold-400 font-semibold mb-10">
          You're not failing. You're using the wrong tool combination.
          Give me 90 days and people will be asking you what the secret is.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg bg-gold-500 text-stone-950 font-semibold text-base hover:bg-gold-400 transition-colors">
            Book a Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a href="/tools" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg border border-stone-700 text-stone-300 font-semibold text-base hover:border-brand-500 hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">
            Explore the ExoPod
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Three Pillars ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-stone-900 border-y border-stone-800">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-stone-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        {[
          { icon: '💪', label: 'Body',   desc: 'Restore your energy, reduce pain, and reset your biology with tools that target the cellular root cause.' },
          { icon: '🧠', label: 'Mind',   desc: 'Build the mindset behind your power. Connect daily action to your deepest vision and start believing in yourself again.' },
          { icon: '✨', label: 'Spirit', desc: 'Build unshakeable faith in yourself as you transform — not just physically, but in every area of life.' },
        ].map(({ icon, label, desc }) => (
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center px-8 py-10 bg-stone-900">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">{icon}</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-2">{label}</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Gary's Story ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-950">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand-400 font-heading font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">About Gary Brandt</p>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-cream-100 mb-6 leading-tight">
            Biohacking Life Coach<br />Medical Weight Loss Coach<br />Pain & Recovery Center Owner
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            After a car accident left me permanently disabled, doctors told me I'd never get my life back.
            I tried fixing my body alone. Then my mind. Then my spirit. Nothing worked until I worked on
            all three at the same time.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            That's when things clicked into place and I saw measurable success in every aspect of my
            life — not just one.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Everything I teach is something I've physically done, experienced, and personally used.
            No theory. No borrowed expertise. Just a complete system that works because it's complete.
          </p>
          <a href="/solutions" class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300 transition-colors">
            See the 90-Day Program &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-stone-800 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-gold-500 to-brand-600 rounded-l-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <blockquote class="text-stone-300 text-lg italic leading-relaxed mb-6 pl-4">
            "I've lived every failure you've lived. I've done every diet, taken every supplement,
            believed every promise that didn't deliver. I don't teach theory — I teach what I've
            personally used to overcome a permanently disabling injury and decades of trauma."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-gold-500 pl-4">— Gary Brandt, Founder of EmpowerX3</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Pain Points ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-900">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-cream-100 mb-3 text-center">
          Traditional Treatments Have Left You With More Questions Than Answers
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-400 text-center mb-10">Does your day look like this?</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-10">
          {[
            'Energy crashes that ruin your afternoons and steal your joy',
            'Pain that makes simple movement feel like punishment',
            'A brain that knows exactly what to do but a body that won\'t cooperate',
            'The quiet shame of being brilliant at everything except the one thing that keeps you alive',
            'Watching your friends struggle and knowing you\'re on the same path',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-stone-800 rounded-xl p-4 border border-stone-700">
              <span class="text-red-500/70 shrink-0 mt-0.5 font-bold" aria-hidden="true">✗</span>
              <span class="text-stone-300">{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="text-center text-lg font-semibold text-gold-400">
          The truth is that <em>you</em> aren't failing. Your current plan is failing <em>you</em>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── ExoPod Intro ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-950">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="bg-stone-900 border border-stone-800 rounded-2xl p-10 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-950/60 to-stone-900" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <span class="text-7xl block mb-4" aria-hidden="true">🛸</span>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-cream-100 mb-1">The ExoPod</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">Lakeway's first all-in-one wellness pod</p>
            <p class="text-gold-400 font-heading font-bold text-xl mt-4">10 Therapies. One Session. Zero Effort.</p>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-1">No Pills. No Needles. No Downtime.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-cream-100 mb-6 leading-tight">
            Reset Your Biology in 30 Minutes
          </h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            EmpowerX3's signature cellular recovery experience. This isn't just another wellness device —
            it's a clinical-grade biohacking tool delivering 10 advanced therapies in one 30-minute session.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Inflammation, slow recovery, and premature aging aren't character flaws. They're cellular problems
            that require cellular solutions. The ExoPod is your reset button.
          </p>
          <a href="/tools" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-brand-600 text-cream-100 font-semibold hover:bg-brand-500 transition-colors">
            See All 10 Therapies &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── CTA Banner ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative bg-brand-900 border-y border-brand-800 py-16 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] opacity-5" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-cream-100 mb-4">
        Ready to Work on All Three at Once?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-brand-300 text-lg mb-3">
        Visit us at Lohman's Crossing in Lakeway, TX — or book a discovery call to start remotely.
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-500 text-sm mb-8">2300 Lohmans Spur #116 · Lakeway, TX 78734</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 rounded-lg bg-gold-500 text-stone-950 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gold-400 transition-colors">
        Book My Free Discovery Call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
